{"tid":816480,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"想講講IPX S R MAX 既相機新功能","createTime":"2018-09-12T18:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T16:28:59.000Z","uid":78533,"like":105,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5cb4b1908acfcad3100907c83a363321a342a0","tid":816480,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 首先睇到真係好驚 二手科技放上發布會<br />\n<br />\n首先 佢個光圈係假的 只係一堆數字唔同***既真光圈變換 效果用法級數都差好遠<br />\n <br />\n而本身個假既淺景深 就係運算出黎 <br />\n<br />\n簡單理解就即係成個背景都係用APP整濛<br />\n<br />\n所以佢既假光圈意思只係濛D同冇咁濛既分別<br />\n<br />\n既然係電子運算出黎既功能 一句講晒 唔係真景深 仲可以整到全黑就係一個好例子<br />\n<br />\n但呢個功能今日先出好明顯係當大家狗咁撚 <br />\n<br />\n點解咁講???<br />\n<br />\n因為依個咁既2手科技 2-5年前大部份好小小既智能手機都有 <br />\n<br />\n但人地仲可以玩埋重新揀對焦位 (當然IPHONE理論上都得 可惜佢冇做到)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係WOR 佢發報會D相真係影得好靚WOR<br />\n<br />\n屌你 咁撚有錢請咁多人番黎 又擺拍又盛 隨手用咩機影都靚啦 唔通是但行過影張咩 咪傻啦 !!!"},{"pid":"0082d55e98b2c5d5310d000668f570ee944038ac","tid":816480,"uid":31475,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:55:54.000Z","msg":"聰明人看破一切<br />\n蠢人付一萬蚊買二手科技<br />\n<br />\n爆炸全是用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99fedfa0034f3b2eaaa6ac1c9d0e6eb9b020020","tid":816480,"uid":49974,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:57:51.000Z","msg":"班死忠係唔會聽得入耳，只會當係新科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13b5336a59262c96cea1a64d8bb430bfb00e806","tid":816480,"uid":78533,"like":21,"dislike":9,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"0082d55e98b2c5d5310d000668f570ee944038ac","tid":816480,"uid":31475,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:55:54.000Z","msg":"聰明人看破一切<br />\n蠢人付一萬蚊買二手科技<br />\n<br />\n爆炸全是用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老實講 成日話***樣 轆7之後安全檢驗做到足<br />\n<br />\n近一兩年到都冇點聽過***有咩安全問題 <br />\n<br />\n但耐唔耐反而IPHONE有咩事 就話用家問題 真係R晒頭"},{"pid":"711325967d040158b9893c1f690fa3919ad68d53","tid":816480,"uid":78533,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:01:56.000Z","msg":"但個疊相技術係勁既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果用落有預期效果的話<br />\n<br />\n不過佢連發報會果幾張相睇落都一般般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪我眼問題"},{"pid":"98cd9031f8caa5f986230d5b40bd81a6583459dc","tid":816480,"uid":49471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:02:53.000Z","msg":"htc m8"},{"pid":"a0db041786e542119f0cbde723379b5829cfff0a","tid":816480,"uid":59408,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"711325967d040158b9893c1f690fa3919ad68d53","tid":816480,"uid":78533,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:01:56.000Z","msg":"但個疊相技術係勁既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果用落有預期效果的話<br />\n<br />\n不過佢連發報會果幾張相睇落都一般般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪我眼問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:03:12.000Z","msg":"Google hdr+ 條 formula 嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b260676fc2e2479ba91acf0e3217b3523a55410e","tid":816480,"uid":78533,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a0db041786e542119f0cbde723379b5829cfff0a","tid":816480,"uid":59408,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"711325967d040158b9893c1f690fa3919ad68d53","tid":816480,"uid":78533,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:01:56.000Z","msg":"但個疊相技術係勁既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl